Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.39,0:00:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.60,0:00:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.71,0:00:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.92,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.72,0:00:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:01:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.44,0:01:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.11,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.75,0:01:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.45,0:01:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.56,0:01:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团\N藉着邀请和平的象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.03,0:01:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为财团的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.33,0:01:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到人们的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.80,0:01:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令世界国家实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.54,0:01:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面，在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗OZ殖民地式支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.88,0:01:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,称为白色獠牙的武装市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.28,0:01:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在各个卫星纷纷起义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.98,0:01:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始了独立运动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.15,0:01:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.52,0:01:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战乱的时代继续进一步加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.29,0:01:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨大变动的一刹那即将出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.47,0:02:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全世界的人请听我讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.30,0:02:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特\N从今日起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.38,0:02:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为罗姆斐拉财团的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.21,0:02:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，这并非为了罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.38,0:02:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是为了令世界的纷争消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.15,0:02:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建立和平的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.19,0:02:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为这是朝着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和各位一起走的最好的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.69,0:02:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,踏出的第一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.19,0:02:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，请你们\N抛掉武器停止斗争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.57,0:02:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位渴望的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.77,0:02:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该一定是相同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.57,0:02:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我一起朝着那未来前进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.24,0:02:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在这里宣布除去\N世界纷争之源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,国家的门户之见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确立把地球当作一个国家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.75,0:02:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[世界国家]宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.97,0:03:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.67,0:03:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十九话\N[特洛瓦回归战场]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果建立了世界国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也就要换工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差劲的玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.16,0:03:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后会更加忙碌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.89,0:03:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为女王陛下的最强兵团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.27,0:03:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即是下一次战斗正等待我们吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.34,0:03:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生你是士兵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不一起走没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祖国消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经没有要保护的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又失去战斗的意义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.94,0:04:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就恢复和平便好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.28,0:04:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样真的没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.51,0:04:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没理由这么轻易就能得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是杰克斯特校吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认错人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.36,0:04:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，你是米利亚尔特大使吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘了自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是为了卫星市民的自由意顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挺身而出的革命斗士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色獠牙的坎斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.41,0:05:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只在卫星革命不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.61,0:05:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要在地球发起革命吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有趣的玩笑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.72,0:05:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是闪电伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.19,0:05:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可惜，我没话和你们说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你们回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.66,0:05:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不信任我们或许也是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只是继承了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.73,0:05:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,领导人希洛‧唯的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以前也会\N作为山克王国的大使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.77,0:05:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自称米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.94,0:05:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解过卫星的独立吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.68,0:05:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.52,0:05:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你再次来宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.72,0:05:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和你的钢弹一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和钢弹一起?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.53,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，钢弹是反抗的象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.43,0:05:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们需要你和钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.61,0:06:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉着莉莉娜女王\N的世界国家宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.78,0:06:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无谓的纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.59,0:06:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将从我们的地球上消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那诚然是高兴的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.76,0:06:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.89,0:06:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的责任并非就此履行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.89,0:06:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了我们曾保护他们的恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.30,0:06:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,显示出反抗意思的叛乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一定要消灭这些叛贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.64,0:06:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令整个地球回复和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题吗?迪尔麦优侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.74,0:06:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么问题?伟列兹公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.71,0:06:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是罗姆斐拉财团的什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.32,0:06:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不大明白你的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.52,0:06:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的新代表兼领导人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.16,0:06:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是莉莉娜女王吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.33,0:07:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.00,0:07:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你站在那里说出今后的方针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.30,0:07:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得那非常不敬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,认为你也应该
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.94,0:07:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和特列斯‧克修里那达一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.57,0:07:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从这财团自动引退的应该不只我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.51,0:07:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我们和你不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不能横蛮地行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.08,0:07:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我提议采用民主表决吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是合理的意见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，为了避免重覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,君主专制带来的历史性错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.80,0:07:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我无意让出现有的地位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然，如果有必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有准备好随时下台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你指现在不是那时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.91,0:07:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样说能得你明白了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伟列兹公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.52,0:08:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果世界就此回复和平…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.60,0:08:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优侯爵想维护自己的地位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.40,0:08:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才全面拥立莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.87,0:08:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而令他自己的地位动摇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，在罗姆斐拉财团之内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.28,0:08:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜女王的支持者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也已经超过半数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.92,0:08:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们希望莉莉娜女王成为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名副其实的世界国家君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.69,0:08:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样真的没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为时代应该\N朝着正确方向移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.31,0:08:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?  五飞果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.88,0:09:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有他的生活方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.72,0:09:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁也不能强迫他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，特洛瓦‧巴顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.32,0:09:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有你来了也算值得庆幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.29,0:09:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为没记忆的我没什么作为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.43,0:09:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，和你们一起\N令我感到安慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就此前去\N温拿家的资源卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.61,0:09:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后在那里替沙漠钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行宇宙用最终调整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.98,0:09:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距离很远，拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要拜托你们的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.52,0:09:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，两位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.03,0:09:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自由与和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.97,0:09:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家究竟怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.71,0:10:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前阵子的我也是这样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.55,0:10:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.19,0:10:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本没话和你们说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.96,0:10:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你始终不肯协助我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.33,0:10:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们自有主意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂\N你们以为我会上那种当吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.84,0:10:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.17,0:10:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我们需要钢弹作为象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但很可惜啊，迪欧‧麦斯威尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到钢弹会成为敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.78,0:10:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别真的想惹怒我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.59,0:10:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你想长命百岁的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.92,0:10:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点!走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希尔妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亏他们找到这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们神通广大无处不晓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也一定要离开这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的要走吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.41,0:11:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，我不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.55,0:11:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再令你和这城市有麻烦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.09,0:11:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可以…和你一起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.49,0:11:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.66,0:11:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有参加白色獠牙一途吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.43,0:11:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正也是为了卫星而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.77,0:11:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也可以回去军队再次战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.38,0:11:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得找到自己的生活方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干嘛要走回头路啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.05,0:11:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留心听我讲，希尔妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们不能信赖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.12,0:11:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们和OZ有相同的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.53,0:12:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，这样下去会毫无回报吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果参加白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.80,0:12:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就会被当作英雄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对那种东西没兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.50,0:12:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我永远做死神就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤独的战斗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.95,0:12:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，那是我们选择了的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.95,0:12:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不可以把卫星卷入战争里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.96,0:12:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们太仁慈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我们才能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么是世界国家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.24,0:13:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们以为那种事\N能骗到我们吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.41,0:13:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，西迪兹上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听闻莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.21,0:13:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个真正渴望和平的领导人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.98,0:13:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种女孩怎会有那种力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.15,0:13:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们是OZ，亦是罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.29,0:13:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别看丢一直以来\N压迫我们的实体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.26,0:13:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的卫星是独立了的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使在令地球的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白那一点的意思上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也一定要\N尽快完成这艘战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.74,0:13:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接收了的月面基地怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.71,0:13:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留在兹巴洛夫MD工场里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.91,0:13:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大量比尔哥零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为我们白色獠牙的战力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正稳定进行装修了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.03,0:14:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武装起来的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令这个卫星也被当作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ宇宙军的驻军基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.57,0:14:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而受到白色獠牙的攻击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种战斗最近屡见不鲜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,整个被毁吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.51,0:14:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙朝着错误的方向前进吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.98,0:14:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把武器带来宇宙的\N是旧统一联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.78,0:14:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在卫星制造武器的是从前的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.42,0:14:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,压迫及支配市民的是罗姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.42,0:14:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包括今次白色獠牙的起义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.29,0:14:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全是地球方面埋下的种子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.90,0:14:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被时代玩弄的事态就太可悲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.00,0:14:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从散播的种子长出来的芽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由谁来令它们凋谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐想那样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于是自愿投身罗姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.48,0:15:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们一定要成为帮助她的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.91,0:15:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左翼推进器被毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不识别就攻击吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.79,0:15:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.19,0:15:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟敢随便出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.76,0:15:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你们见识\N我们宇宙军的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士从敌人\N穿梭机里出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.04,0:15:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用密集队型迎击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左翼的MD消灭穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.47,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.04,0:15:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦\N你一个人去太鲁莽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.48,0:15:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像曾经学过，我试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色陶拉斯?何方神圣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厉…厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.33,0:16:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这部穿梭机数分钟后就会自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离开后马上攻击敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好迟纯!沙漠钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里就是极限吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.28,0:17:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?是钢弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.92,0:17:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色獠牙得到钢弹吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.99,0:17:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,散开!散开包围他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.37,0:18:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔!你想做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部穿梭机要爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以这部沙漠钢弹的推进器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会赶不及去特洛瓦那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.99,0:18:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碰碰运气!我要试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯萨琳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.49,0:19:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面对机械，你们真不像样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实在是好人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.13,0:19:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地狱死神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.69,0:19:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我要救曾毁掉你的家伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.76,0:20:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?你忘了我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是你珍贵的好朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说笑啊，说笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真没趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.47,0:21:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧，你肯和我们一起战斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.98,0:21:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，因为战斗的只有我们就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.32,0:21:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧‧麦斯威尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.92,0:21:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我衷心感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别有太大期望比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.96,0:21:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我会马上令你失望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.99,0:21:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那家伙死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.59,0:21:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界国家和这种虚假的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.19,0:22:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就能被消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.20,0:22:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.20,0:22:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要杀死你
